'''Central African Repabliki''' ('''CAR''') ke naga lefasaneng la [[Afrika]]. CAR e bogare ba [[Afrika]], e wela seleteng sa [[Bogare ba Afrika|Bogare Ba Afrika]].


CAR e agišane le :
* [[Chad]] (leboa),
* [[Sudan]] (bohlabela), 
* [[Republic ya Congo]] (borwa),
* [[Democratic Republic of the Congo]] (borwa), 
* [[Cameroon]] (bodikela).

CAR ke e tee ya dinaga tše hlano [[Afrika]], [[landlocked|tšeo di sa bapago le lewatle]].

